name: Rare Screemu
description: It's not often that a full-grown Gigacheep soars overhead... but when it happens, it's an experience not easily forgotten. That must've been what happened to inspire the design of the Rare Screemu; the Monster would like to think that it was a spitting image of the fledgling form of the avian Titan... but in truth, it's a bird-brained notion that it could ever pass for anything other than a Rare Wublin.
breedingCombo: None. Zap The Contents, And Power Up!
polarity: Negative from: Rare Pixolotl, Positive From: Rare Creepuscule, Negative toward: Rare Zuuker, Positive toward: Rare Blipsqueak
